rComments: Valentine is the only prof I actually enjoy listening to. That says a lot coming from a fourth year university student. He makes everything very clear, and sound interesting, even if it isn't. Also provided the most fair test questions I have ever had. I wish I had known about Valentine earlier, I recommend taking a class with this prof!

Professor Valentine is really awesome. He's very engaging and passionate, which makes even boring lectures enjoyable (ie. sometimes dry material). His grading is also very fair and accurately reflects the effort you put in. If you show up to class, pay attention, and spend some time studying, you'll do great on his tests. He never tricks you.
